fn.p:
As previously mentioned, our data set covers net purchases (or sales) by foreign investors in the domestic spot equity markets for each of the six countries in our sample. However, although such data start on January 1992, both equity return and flows data are simultaneously available for all six countries only from March 1996. To accommodate these limitations, the variables
